file.name: sampleWithMinimumValues.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers: []
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Very simple
paths:
  /pets:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: query
          name: limit
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
            minimum: 0
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Returns all the pets
components:
  schemas:
    Cat:
      x-extension-here: 'yes'
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
